                <mxCell id="uc_folio" value="&lt;b&gt;CreateFolioUseCase&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;implements CreateFolioInputPort&lt;br&gt;─────────────────────&lt;br&gt;- quoteRepo: QuoteRepositoryPort&lt;br&gt;- coreService: CoreServicePort&lt;br&gt;─────────────────────&lt;br&gt;+ execute(subscriberId, agentCode): FolioResult&lt;br&gt;  1. coreService.generateFolio(year)&lt;br&gt;  2. si folio existe → return 200 (idempotente)&lt;br&gt;  3. quoteRepo.save(new Quote(folio, CREATED))" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;spacingLeft=6;" parent="1" vertex="1">
