                <mxCell id="uc_calc" value="&lt;b&gt;CalculatePremiumUseCase&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;implements CalculatePremiumInputPort&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;GoF: Strategy — delega cálculo por cobertura&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;─────────────────────&lt;br&gt;- quoteRepo: QuoteRepositoryPort&lt;br&gt;- coreService: CoreServicePort&lt;br&gt;- strategies: List&lt;PremiumCalculationStrategy&gt;&lt;br&gt;─────────────────────&lt;br&gt;+ execute(folio, version): PremiumResult&lt;br&gt;  1. quoteRepo.findByFolio(folio)&lt;br&gt;  2. coreService.getTariffs(criteria)&lt;br&gt;  3. por cada location calculable:&lt;br&gt;     breakdown = strategies.map(s→s.calculate(loc, tariff))&lt;br&gt;     netPremium = breakdown.total()&lt;br&gt;  4. commercialPremium = netPremium × factor&lt;br&gt;  5. quote.updatePremium(result)&lt;br&gt;  6. quoteRepo.update(quote)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;spacingLeft=6;" parent="1" vertex="1">
